e=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>24 часа</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>от 120 руб</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>&nbsp;1 чел/час</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;2.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong class=\"style23\"><a href=\"http://taggerd.su/page/0/4/\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">Оснащение объектов техническими</span></span></span></a></strong></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong class=\"style23\"><a href=\"http://taggerd.su/page/0/4/\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">системами безопасности</span></span></span></a></strong></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong class=\"style23\"><a href=\"http://taggerd.su/page/0/4/\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">и охраны </span></span></span></a></strong></span></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>Монтаж,</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>обслуживание, гарантия</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>ремонт</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080\">Договорная</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;3.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong class=\"style23\">Сопровождение грузов при </strong><strong class=\"style23\">транспортировке по ж/д или</strong> <strong class=\"style23\">автотранспортом </strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong class=\"style23\">С оружием,</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong class=\"style23\">без учета накладных расходов</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>от 250 руб</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>1 чел/час</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;4.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong class=\"style23\">Сопровождение МЦ </strong><strong class=\"style23\">и</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong class=\"style23\">денежных средств при перевозке </strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">Спец-автомобиль +</span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">два охранника с оружием</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </strong></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>не менее</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>4 часа</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080\">от 2000 руб</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>за&nbsp;1 час</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;5.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>Мероприятия по выявлению</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>каналов утечки информации</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>и защите КТ </strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>Договорная</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;6.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>Консультирование по вопросам безопасности</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>и охраны</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;Договорная</span></strong></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;7.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>Личная охрана</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>(телохранители)</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"middle\" bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>На постоянной&nbsp;основе</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"middle\" bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>не менее</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>8&nbsp;час/дн</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"middle\" bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>от 300 руб</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td valign=\"middle\" bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"center\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>1 чел/час</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>На разовой&nbsp;основе </strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>не менее</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>4 часа</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>от 500 руб</strong></span></span></span></td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>1 чел/час</strong></span></span></span></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;8.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ccccf