\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>от 500 руб</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ccccff\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;<strong>1 чел/час</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">&nbsp;9.</span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" align=\"left\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\" rowspan=\"2\">\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>Обеспечение безопасности</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        <div><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>при проведении массовых мероприятий </strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><strong>Концерты, праздники, собрания, спортивные мероприятия, выставки и др.</strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td bordercolor=\"#6600ff\" bgcolor=\"#ffffcc\">\r\n                        <div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-small\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #