an></strong></span></span></span></div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><font size=\"2\">&diams; </font></span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-color: #ccffff\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\">VIP-охранник (от 185 см и от 90 кг) - <a href=\"http://taggerd.su/\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">охрана объектов</span></a> повышенной сложности и элитных заведений</span></span></span></strong></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">&diams;</span><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"> </span><span style=\"background-color: #ccffff\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">Охранник (на суточный, дневной, ночной&nbsp;&nbsp;вахтовый режим работы, для&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000080\">охраны объектов</span>&nbsp;с оружием и/или без оружия, на стационарные объекты и для сопровождения грузов при перевозке)</span></span></span></span></strong></div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\"><strong><span><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"background-color: #ccffff\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff\">&diams;</span></span></span></span></span></strong></span><strong><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"background-color: #ccffff\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"background-color: #ffffff\">&nbsp;</span>Охранник -кинолог (<a href=\"http://taggerd.su/page/5/21/\"><span style=\"color: #000080\">охрана с собаками</span></a>)</span></span></span></span></strong></div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">&diams;</span><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><font size=\"2\">&nbsp;</font></span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-color: #ccffff\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><font size=\"2\">С</font></span></span></span>отрудник в группу быстрого реагирования (ГБР)</span></span></span></span></strong></div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">&diams;</span>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: #ccffff\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\">Водитель, водитель-телохранитель, водитель-инкассатор</span></span></span></span></strong></div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #0000ff\">&diams;</span><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><font size=\"2\"> </font></span></span></span></span><span style=\"background-color: #ccffff\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><span style=\"color: #000080\"><span style=\"font-size: larger\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial\"><font size=\"2\">Т</fo